quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"Do you [Prophet] not see how your Lord dealt with the army of the elephant?"
  105,2,"Did He not utterly confound their plans?"
  105,3,"He sent ranks of birds against them,"
  105,4,"pelting them with pellets of hard-baked clay:"
  105,5,"He made them [like] cropped stubble."
